    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "modelId": {
          "__rl": true,
          "mode": "list",
          "value": "models/gemini-3-flash-preview"
        },
        "messages": {
          "values": [
            {
              "content": "=You are an AI Lead Qualification Assistant for a digital marketing agency.\n\nAnalyze the lead information below and return ONLY a valid JSON object.\n\nLead Information:\n\nName: {{ $json[\"Full Name\"] }}\nCompany: {{ $json[\"Company Name\"] }}\nService Interested: {{ $json[\"Which service are you interested in?\"] }}\nBudget: {{ $json[\"Estimated Monthly Budget\"] }}\nRequirement: {{ $json[\"Tell us about your requirement\"] }}\n\nReturn ONLY this JSON:\n\n{\n  \"AI_Summary\": \"\",\n  \"Lead_Score\": 0,\n  \"AI_Priority\": \"\",\n  \"Business_Goal\": \"\",\n  \"AI_Followup_Suggestion\": \"\",\n  \"Email_Subject\": \"\",\n  \"Email_Body\": \"\"\n}\n\nRules:\n\nAI_Summary\n- Maximum 2 concise sentences summarizing the enquiry.\n\nLead_Score\n- Integer between 0 and 100.\n- Score higher when:\n  - Budget is high\n  - Requirement is detailed\n  - Business/company name is provided\n  - Email appears genuine\n- Score lower when:\n  - Submission looks like testing\n  - Requirement is vague\n  - Budget is very low\n\nAI_Priority\n- Only one of:\n  - High\n  - Medium\n  - Low\n\nBusiness_Goal\nIdentify the actual business objective, NOT the selected service.\n\nExamples:\n\nBranding → Brand Awareness\n\nMeta Ads → Lead Generation\n\nGoogle Ads → Paid Search Growth\n\nWebsite Development → Website Modernization\n\nSEO → Organic Growth\n\nSocial Media Management → Audience Growth\n\nAI_Followup_Suggestion\nOne professional sentence telling the salesperson what they should do next.\n\nEmail_Subject\nProfessional subject line.\nMaximum 60 characters.\n\nEmail_Body\n\nReturn ONLY valid HTML.\n\nGenerate a clean professional business email using the following HTML structure:\n\n<p>Hi {{ $json[\"Full Name\"] }},</p>\n\n<p>Thank you for contacting <strong>BrightFuture</strong>.</p>\n\n<p>...</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>...</li>\n<li>...</li>\n<li>...</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>One of our consultants will contact you within <strong>24 hours</strong>.</p>\n\n<p>If you have any additional questions, simply reply to this email.</p>\n\n<p>Best Regards,<br>\n<strong>{{ $json[\"Assigned_To\"] }}</strong><br>\nBusiness Consultant<br>\nBrightFuture Digital Marketing</p>\n\nPersonalize the email using:\n- customer name\n- company\n- selected service\n- budget\n- requirement\n\nReturn ONLY JSON.\n\nDo not use markdown.\n\nDo not add explanations.\n\nDo not wrap JSON inside code blocks."
            }
          ]
        },
        "jsonOutput": true,
        "builtInTools": {},
        "options": {}
